1.腾讯AI语音合成text字符串带感叹号、空格等，sign会无效
2.返回的base64可以直接通过new Buffer(data,'base64')解码并写入mp3文件
3.数据库设计
    users
        openid : only key,
        blindMode: open or close blind mode,
        points: the points users have gotten,
        {ref:idea,comment,recommendation}
    
    ideas
        {author : author's openid},
        {recommendation: the id of recommendation},
        {comments: the comments}
        date: upload date, time stamp,
        content: idea content,
        soundFragments: the number or name of clips of long sound file's fragments,
        points: the points this idea has gotten,
        dislike: count the number of who dislike this idea
        {ref:user,recommendation,comment}

    comments
        {ideaID: idea},
        {author: author's openid},
        date: time stamp
        soundFragments: the number or name of clips of long sound file's fragments,
        {ref:user,idea}

    stars
        starID: id,
        des: describtion,
        soundFragments: the number or name of clips of long sound file's fragments

    recommendations
        type: type, [text,news,music,book]
        detail: detail,
            {
            //type=music
                name:
                author: 
                url:
                comments:
            //text
                cover:
                content:
                author:
            //news
                cover:
                content:
                author:
            }
        soundFragments: the number or name of clips of long sound file's fragments,
        date: date,
        starId
        {ref:user,idea}
    
4.把赤经值转换成时角分制度，时的数值加上6就是最佳观测月份。
在北半球，如果|本地纬度-天体赤纬|>90，是看不到天体的。